page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the REST API'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with the REST API.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI Service resource with either the `gpt-35-turbo` or the `gpt-4` models deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.
